As i speak i am writing to the dev team.<br>
<br>
To people who say they should remove the skill. Come on! Let VI remove any skill which we are good at? <br>
<br>
Infact, i bet many of you are actually mages in disguise, saying you are happy that wizards suck and that we should have our class abilities removed. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=elyia>Elyia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 220<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/4/03 12:57 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A request to have manaburn looked at.</span><hr size=1> I don't know what to tell you if you think Wizards suck.  But hey I'm doing just fine without Manaburn. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~kosmos00/elyiasig.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:xx-small;"><br>
-Arcanist-<br>
.<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=42264">Profile</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.:.<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.keepersofthefaith.org">KTF</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aarell>aarell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/4/03 1:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A request to have manaburn looked at.</span><hr size=1> Wizards don't suck. Doesn't mean I wouldn't want to have manaburn back, and no, who ever thinks I'm talking about farming Velious and Kunark, just go away. Your statement is patronizing at best, and condescending beyound belief. The gentlemen has a point. It would be darn nice to have MB back, I for one would love to be able to crit again in the 15K to 20K range, when say MM or Bert is enraging, and our tanks can't strike back, I'd be more than happy to blast the hell out of em then. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=myztic>MyztiC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Born-Again Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 666<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/4/03 1:28 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A request to have manaburn looked at.</span><hr size=1> Do you have 100% or close mana when MM or Bert enrage?<br>
<br>
-myz <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aarell>aarell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/4/03 1:51 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A request to have manaburn looked at.</span><hr size=1> As Manaburn stands now, absolutly not, if it were changed back to what it was, and say a small wiz team of 3 were put together, such that they started medding when Bert was at 25% to get back to full, it would make sense to me. In general when we do Bert, we have from 6 to 10 wizzes on. Change the way MB works back to what it was, and wizzies will change the way they fight. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=luxum>Luxum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>Pics plz thx :(</span><br>  Posts: 1999<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/4/03 1:58 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A request to have manaburn looked at.</span><hr size=1> It absolutely cannot be restored to what it was in the Luclin era, it would completely break PoP and return us to incredibly boring &quot;bazillion hp, hope your clerics don't fall asleep during the rotation&quot; type encounters.  However i think it's reasonable to ask that they modify it so that it can crit like it used to, but retain the one wizard at a time restriction.  When they explained how they were nerfing it, they never mentioned that it would not crit as strongly. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.sillyjanine.com/mybases.html"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.cestusdei.org/uploads/images/luxysig.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aarell>aarell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/4/03 2:07 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A request to have manaburn looked at.</span><hr size=1> with a minute wait, it would still be useless, drop that down to 10 or 15 secs, yep then it wouild be worthwhile. As to boring, I never noticed our clerics getting bored in the CH teams, but then 5 clerics during bert probably don't get bored. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=myztic>MyztiC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Born-Again Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 669<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/4/03 2:10 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A request to have manaburn looked at.</span><hr size=1> CH chains during Bert are like 1/10 compared to Luclin. 45 minute fights in beginning of Luclin with mana rodding and stuff... were not exciting or fun. Even the emperor ssra nowadays with 15 minute fight is boring after PoP's short and more unforgiving ones.<br>
<br>
-myz <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aarell>aarell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/4/03 2:33 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A request to have manaburn looked at.</span><hr size=1> Boring = subjective, reduce the number of clerics low enough, and anything can become interesting, but then again, that's subjective on my part, as to what I find to be non-boring. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mirakules>Mirakules</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/4/03 4:59 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Just coz...</span><hr size=1> Bah, there are so many mages in disguise here it stinks.<br>
I like all abilities that gives my class an edge. If you disagree with that you are obviously a mage lurking our wizs boards. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=midgetgod>Midget God</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 273<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/5/03 10:12 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just coz...</span><hr size=1> Wizards don't nuke 25points better. I did 47k to Telk last night using draught of ro. I did 42k to Burrower Parasite. How is this lame? <p>[63 Sorcerer] <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=69194">Zuratuli</a> (Gnome)</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gwideonthegnome>GwideonTheGnome</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 89<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/5/03 11:29 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just coz...</span><hr size=1> Gnomish Greetings!<br>
