In its current state, MB isn't worth the AA XP. Before, yes it sucked mana, but still it was usuable in some situations, now it isn't.<br>
<br>
So tell me, what is the point in this AA ability?<br>
As in &quot;whats the point in Al'Kabor?&quot;<br>
